## 7. **Cancellation Token Pattern**

Used in long-running operations:

```typescript
// Service-level cancellation
private isCancelled = false;

async fetchAndProcessOrderData(...): Promise<void> {
  for (let year = startYear; year <= endYear; year++) {
    if (this.isCancelled) {
      this.logger.warn('Processing cancelled', { year });
      break;
    }
    await this.processYearData({ year, monthsToProcess });
  }
}

cancelOperation(): void {
  this.isCancelled = true;
}

resetCancellation(): void {
  this.isCancelled = false;
}
